---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const seo = {
  title: "Rekord24 | Anna Kocaj",
  description:
    "Designing an app that lets users handle administrative matters online.",
  image: "/ratusz_thumbnail.png",
};
---

<Layout seo={seo}>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="mt-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6">
    <a
      href="/projects"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 opacity-50 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity text-sm mb-8"
    >
      ← Back to projects
    </a>

    <p class="text-sm opacity-50 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 font-medium">
      Case Study · 2025
    </p>
    <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-4 leading-snug">Ratusz24</h1>
    <a
      href="https://www.figma.com/design/hg6OXZEUo9l93fwVthJW60/Ratusz-24?node-id=70-13130&t=eVXLcJ2WosdDdhgn-1"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="group/link inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 hover:border-accent transition-all duration-300 mb-4 w-fit"
    >
      View in Figma
      <span
        aria-hidden="true"
        class="transition-transform duration-300 group-hover/link:translate-x-0.5"
        >→</span
      >
    </a>
    <p class="text-lg opacity-70 mb-8 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
      An app that lets users handle administrative matters online.
    </p>

    <!-- Overview grid -->
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4 py-6 border-t border-b border-white/10 mb-10"
    >
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-1">My Role</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium">Product Designer</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-1">
          Timeline
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium">20 hours</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-1">
          Design Tools
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium">Figma</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero image -->
    <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden m-6 bg-gray-800">
      <Image
        src="/ratusz_thumbnail.png"
        alt="Ratusz24 on dekstop and mobile"
        width={1200}
        height={675}
        class="w-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CHALLENGE -->
  <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-4">The Challenge</h2>
    <p class="opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Municipal services like car registration or driver's license renewal are
      essential, but scattered across confusing government sites and buried in
      bureaucratic language. Most residents don't know which department handles
      what they need, let alone where to find it online.
    </p>
    <p class="opacity-70 leading-relaxed">
      The challenge was to design a single platform, built for municipalities
      representing <strong>1.6M residents</strong>, where anyone, regardless of
      age or comfort with technology, could find and start the right service in
      minutes.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- PROCESS -->
  <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-8">Process</h2>

    <div class="space-y-12">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div>
        <p
          class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-2 font-medium"
        >
          01 — Define
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-base mb-3">
          Two ways of not knowing what you need
        </h3>
        <p class="opacity-70 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Residents fall into two groups: people who know exactly what they're
          looking for ("driver's license renewal") and people who only know
          their situation ("I just moved here, what do I need to do?"). A single
          search bar serves the first group well and fails the second. The
          platform needed to support both without forcing either one through the
          other's path.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div>
        <p
          class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-2 font-medium"
        >
          02 — Concept
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-base mb-3">
          An intelligent search, and a wizard for everyone else
        </h3>
        <p class="opacity-70 leading-relaxed text-sm mb-4">
          For residents who already know the service name, an intelligent search
          engine surfaces car registration, driver's license, and other services
          instantly.
        </p>
        <div class="rounded-l overflow-hidden m-6 bg-gray-800">
          <Image
            src="/ratusz_1.png"
            alt="Ratusz24 intelligent search"
            width={1200}
            height={675}
            class="w-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="opacity-70 leading-relaxed text-sm mb-4">
          For everyone else, a short wizard asks a few plain-language questions
          about their situation and guides them to the right service.
        </p>
        <div class="rounded-l overflow-hidden m-6 bg-gray-800">
          <Image
            src="/ratusz_3.png"
            alt="Ratusz24 service wizard"
            width={1200}
            height={675}
            class="w-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div>
        <p
          class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-2 font-medium"
        >
          03 — Design & Prototype
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-base mb-3">
          Intuitive by default, on any device
        </h3>
        <p class="opacity-70 leading-relaxed text-sm mb-4">
          Because Ratusz24 needed to work for residents of all ages and digital
          literacy levels, I kept the interface deliberately simple and followed
          established design conventions rather than reinventing patterns. The full experience was designed
          responsively.
        </p>
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden m-6 bg-gray-800">
          <Image
            src="/ratusz_2.png"
            alt="Ratusz24 responsive design across devices"
            width={1200}
            height={675}
            class="w-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- OUTCOMES -->
    <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-6">Outcomes</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">🏆 1st</p>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-60">place, RekordSI, January 2025</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">1.6M</p>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-60">
            residents representing target audience
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-gray-800">
          <Image
            src="/ratusz_prize.jpeg"
            alt="Ania getting a prize for winning Ratusz24"
            width={1200}
            height={675}
            class="w-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
    </section>
    

    <!-- NAVIGATION -->
    <section
      class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16 flex justify-center items-center border-t border-white/10 pt-8"
    >
      <a
        href="/projects"
        class="opacity-50 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity text-sm"
      >
        ← All projects
      </a>
    </section>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  strong {
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  em {
    color: inherit;
  }
</style>
